        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>Nov. 27<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></date>
                    <salute>My dear Bowman</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>Very many thanks for your note.<ref target="#foot.f2"/> As the disease is not very rare, &amp; as it is known to be hereditary, I will not give the case, (about which I was very doubtful) &amp; am glad to decide in the negative. My informant has a name which could fill up one of these lines by its length, &amp; which was the reason I did not copy it letter by letter.<ref target="#foot.f3"/></p>
<p>Your’s most sincerely | Ch. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
            
        </div>

        

        

