            <note xml:id="foot.f3">CD probably refers <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_2155.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Hermanus Hartogh Heijs van Zouteveen</ref>, and his letter of 2 March 1871 (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1581.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi></ref> vol. 19). See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-9161.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from William Bowman, 26 November 1873</ref> and n. 1.</note>
